# Agent coordination files — read live from disk by the ttyview hub
# page; not for upstream consumption. Kept local. (AGENT_LOG.md was
# renamed from AGENTS.md to avoid clashing with the well-known
# AGENTS.md convention used by other agent frameworks for instruction
# files — same name, different purpose, too confusing.)
STATUS.md
AGENT_LOG.md
